{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"categories":1,"event_categories":27},[2,9,15,21],{"id":3,"attributes":4},1,{"slug":5,"name":6,"description":7,"createdAt":8,"updatedAt":8},"nutrition","營養隨筆",null,"2023-02-07T08:03:25.893Z",{"id":10,"attributes":11},2,{"slug":12,"name":13,"description":7,"createdAt":14,"updatedAt":14},"spiritual","心靈勵志","2023-02-07T08:03:25.896Z",{"id":16,"attributes":17},3,{"slug":18,"name":19,"description":7,"createdAt":20,"updatedAt":20},"fitness","運動筆記","2023-02-07T08:03:25.905Z",{"id":22,"attributes":23},4,{"slug":24,"name":25,"description":7,"createdAt":26,"updatedAt":26},"reflection","感悟隨筆","2023-02-07T08:03:25.906Z",[28,33,38,43,47,52],{"id":3,"attributes":29},{"name":30,"slug":31,"description":7,"createdAt":32,"updatedAt":32},"名人面對面","be-our-guess","2023-02-07T08:03:24.223Z",{"id":10,"attributes":34},{"name":35,"slug":36,"description":7,"createdAt":37,"updatedAt":37},"文化導賞","cultural","2023-02-07T08:03:24.230Z",{"id":16,"attributes":39},{"name":40,"slug":41,"description":7,"createdAt":42,"updatedAt":42},"遊山玩水","hiking","2023-02-07T08:03:24.235Z",{"id":22,"attributes":44},{"name":45,"slug":5,"description":7,"createdAt":46,"updatedAt":46},"活學營養","2023-02-07T08:03:24.241Z",{"id":48,"attributes":49},5,{"name":50,"slug":18,"description":7,"createdAt":51,"updatedAt":51},"健體運動","2023-02-07T08:03:24.256Z",{"id":53,"attributes":54},6,{"name":55,"slug":56,"description":7,"createdAt":57,"updatedAt":57},"讀書會","book-sharing","2023-02-07T08:03:24.257Z"],"uses":{"dependencies":["http://localhost:1337/api/categories?","http://localhost:1337/api/event-categories?"]},"slash":"always"},{"type":"data","data":[{"id":1,"attributes":2},792,{"title":3,"excerpt":4,"content":5,"slug":6,"createdAt":7,"updatedAt":7,"author":8,"categories":9,"tags":17,"image":39,"related_posts":40},"“被運動”，有效用？（下篇）",null,"\n\n上星期解構了冷凍溶脂，今次我們來了解家用瘦身儀的成效😉。\n\n家用瘦身儀大多採用EMS (Electrical Muscle Stimulation)技術：聲稱以低頻微電流向神經發出微電流信號，即使沒有運動，都可以通過微電流的刺激，令肌肉達到運動效果，繼而瘦身。\n\n肌肉訓練器（俗稱“\n腹肌貼\"）💪🏻則是把帶有電極的腰帶或貼片固定在身體上，透過電流刺激，給肌肉施加負荷，大多用於復健及物理治療上。\n\n確實有不少職業運動員，透過EMS加強訓練效果。例如仰臥起坐時，將儀器貼於腹部，令人更著意腹部動作，有助收緊線條。\n\n然而，肌肉訓練器或其他EMS儀器均沒有燒脂效果。脂肪細胞的分解，與物理性的刺激無關；而單靠電流建立肌肉，必須使用極高電流，人體難以承受。\n\n“被動式運動”，看起來身體在動，但其實只在耗電，並不能提升熱量消耗😅。只有運用肌肉力量去活動身體時，才可真正提高能量消耗及脂肪燃燒的速率。","weight-loss-210811","2021-08-11T00:00:00.000Z",{"data":4},{"data":10},[11],{"id":12,"attributes":13},1,{"slug":14,"name":15,"description":4,"createdAt":16,"updatedAt":16},"nutrition","營養隨筆","2023-02-07T08:03:25.893Z",{"data":18},[19,24,29,34],{"id":20,"attributes":21},132,{"name":22,"createdAt":23,"updatedAt":23},"瘦身","2023-02-07T08:03:10.800Z",{"id":25,"attributes":26},133,{"name":27,"createdAt":28,"updatedAt":28},"肌肉","2023-02-07T08:03:10.804Z",{"id":30,"attributes":31},112,{"name":32,"createdAt":33,"updatedAt":33},"脂肪","2023-02-07T08:03:10.608Z",{"id":35,"attributes":36},122,{"name":37,"createdAt":38,"updatedAt":38},"減肥","2023-02-07T08:03:10.721Z",{"data":4},{"data":41},[]],"uses":{"dependencies":["http://localhost:1337/api/posts?populate[author]=true&populate[categories]=true&populate[tags]=true&populate[image]=true&populate[related_posts]=true&filters[slug][$eq]=weight-loss-210811"],"params":["slug"]}}]}